beer.beer_description:
Sure summer is great, but an Indian Summer goes on forever. You get those perfect days when the heat is just right and you can enjoy long, lazy afternoons, soaking up the warmth from tropical reaches. Crisp & light in bitterness with aromas of passionfruit & honeydew, light in alcohol and body, but not at the expense of hop character. To be enjoyed now and long after the sun’s gone down.

Hops: Equinox and Galaxy

Malts: Pale ale and wheat
